Total Commander 7.55 RC2  


altTotal Commander is a file manager replacement that offers multiple language 

support, search, file comparison, directory synchronization, quick view panel with 

bitmap display, ZIP, ARJ, LZH, RAR, UC2, TAR, GZ, CAB, ACE archive handling plus 

plugins, built-in FTP client with FXP, HTTP proxy support, and more.
